{
  "texts": [
    "We categorise feedback into two main types based on the methods of collection.",
    "One is APP usage data, which is automatically collected by the APP, including the frequency of use for each function, overall usage duration, and the number of times used.",
    "The other type is userprovided feedback, comprising the frequency of users' Auslan communication, satisfaction with the progress of their Auslan learning, and subjective user comments.",
    "Statistical data, such as app usage metrics, the frequency of users signing Auslan, and user satisfaction levels, can be summarised and analysed.",
    "Subjective user comments include not only users' suggestions and opinions but also issues raised during usage."
  ]
}